---
interface Props {
  headingId?: string;
}

const { headingId = "reading-library-heading" } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="ask-leilia-section ask-leilia-reading-library" aria-labelledby={headingId}>
  <h2 id={headingId}>See How I Read</h2>
  <p>
    Before choosing a reading, you're welcome to explore a selection of recent client readings.
  </p>
  <p>
    Every reading is personally interpreted by Leilia and published only with permission or
    appropriate anonymisation. They are not marketing examples or AI-generated samples. They are
    genuine readings that demonstrate how I work, how I interpret the cards, and the depth of
    insight you can expect.
  </p>
  <p>
    Reading a few examples is often the best way to decide whether my approach is the right fit for
    you.
  </p>
  <a class="ask-leilia-pricing__cta ask-leilia-reading-library__cta" href="/recent-client-readings/">
    Browse the Reading Library
  </a>
</section>
